text: Wilfred Burne (13 May 1903 - 12 August 1989) was a British diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1989 deaths Category:British male divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
